name: AFL integrity unit investigates Crows player over alleged homophobic slur
description: AFL Adelaide Crows player Izak Rankine could be banned for the remainder of the AFL season as the integrity unit investigates allegations of a homophobic slur.

name: Sydney woman loses life savings to text scam
description: A legal expert has warned it's no longer possible for bank customers to protect themselves from scams after a Sydney woman lost her life savings to a sophisticated text message fraud.

name: Husband
description: A blue Mustang, which was used as a getaway car in a Sydney fatal shooting, has been found torched. With police saying the victim of the shooting, a husband and a young girl was not the intended target.

name: Growing concerns for Rottnest Island's environment
description: There are growing concerns that developments on Rottnest Islands are coming at the expense of the environment.

name: Zelensky to meet with Trump; Qantas hit with major fine over sacking staff
description: Volodymyr Zelensky will join Donald Trump for peace talks, just days after the American leader failed to secure a ceasefire agreement with Vladimir Putin.
